cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.CY, cs.NI

The paper discusses methods for preventing, detecting, and reacting to ICT attacks and failures in the electric power system. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper touches on cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and network infrastructure (cs.NI) as it discusses the integration of ICT in the power system and the potential effects of failures or attacks on system stability.
